message.content:
Kia ora! Tēnā koa whakapā mai ki a au i ngā whakaputanga tino whakamārama. Ka taea e au te āwhina i a koe ki te whakatutuki i ēnei whakarārangi. Tēnā, whakaputa mai ō whakapākenga i te reo Māori, kaua e whakamāori, ā, ka whakautu ahau i ō whakapātai i te reo Māori.

1. Ki te pirati i te raupapa rorohiko:
   - Pāwhiritia te pūtātara o te raupapa rorohiko.
   - Pāwhiritia te whiriwhiri "Pirati" (hoatu he tuku i te matapihi whakahaere rorohiko).
   - Pāwhiritia te whiriwhiri "Whakamahia" (ka whakapau kaha i te pirati).
   - Whakararuraru i te raupapa rorohiko kia whakamutua te pirati.
   - Kia mahara ki te whakapau kaha i tō raupapa rorohiko ki te āwhina ki te whakatutuki i te mahi tino hōu.

2. Ki te tohatoha i te ipurangi:
   - Whakateretia tō pūtirotiro rorohiko.
   - Tūwhera i tētahi tūmau pūtirotiro (whakamahia he pūtirotiro whakahaere rorohiko).
   - Pāwhiritia te whiriwhiri "Tuhinga" (hoatu he tukanga hei tohatoha i te ipurangi).
   - Whakararuraru i ngā āhuatanga whakararuraru me te whakamutu i te tohatoha i te ipurangi.
   - Kia whakararuraru i te tohatoha, whakamahia he kaha whakapau kaha rorohiko me te āwhina
